# TOM.quest Project Context

Personal website for Tom Heffernan, PhD student in AI at WPI.

## IMPORTANT: Whenever you fix something add info about it here so the issue is not repeated. Whenever you change something update this doc so it stays up to date. 

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 16 with App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4 (PostCSS-based, no tailwind.config)
- Geist fonts (Sans + Mono)
- Hosted on Vercel

## Design System
- Background: pure black (#000)
- Text: white (#fff), reduced opacity for secondary (white/60, white/40)
- Animations: fade-in with translateY, defined in globals.css
- Navigation: fixed top bar, underline on active page
- Layout: max-w-3xl centered container, generous whitespace

