## Turing Dashboard
- Frontend calls `/api/turing/*` routes which proxy to FastAPI on Turing
- Backend connects via Cloudflare Tunnel (quick tunnel or named)
- Env vars: `TURING_API_URL`, `TURING_API_KEY` (Vercel); `API_KEY` (Turing .env)
- Max 12 GPU allocations enforced in backend
- GPU types: nvidia=H100, tesla=V100
- Allocation params: time (mins), memory (MB, default 64000), count (1-12), project_dir
- Job name: "tom.quest" (set via --job-name)
- Project dir selection: browse Turing dirs, first command is `cd {project_dir}`
- Saved commands: stored per-project in localStorage (`turing_project_commands`)
- Screen naming: `tq_{project_name}_{index}` (reuses screens, not per-job)

